TEXT.S: Cameron Bairstow, unu syubaykanasmalimiunduaynu Amilika NBA nisakaput, u tabakiay ayaway mimaliay/ tebanay mimaliay. Cameron Bairstow i 1914 a mihcaan NBA sapapili'mimaliay a kawaw, saka 2 ku uwac atu silsil 49, namapili' tu nu Chicago Bulls putiput. 12 bulad 7 demiad, 1990 a mihca, Cameron Bairstow, miunduay.
